---
title: Seared Beef & Caramelised Onion Panini with Fries & Creamy Pesto
description: When making a panini sandwich you want to have the best flavour combos in town. Beef strips, caramelised onion and a creamy pesto dressing has to be the winner because we can’t get enough of them!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/seared-beef-caramelised-onion-paninis-87d3972d.jpg
